*   ## **_SANTOS ESCOBAR DEF. APOLLO CREWS_**
    

Fun match. Short but Apollo looked great in small bursts.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/35ccb8e3-4550-4004-973c-7d1bb562651b/20240802_182514.jpg?format=original)

*   ## **_WWE WOMEN'S TAG TEAM CHAMPIONSHIPS: JADE CARGILL AND BIANCA BELAIR DEF. UNHOLY UNION BY DQ_**
    

Blair Davenport attacks Jade to cause a DQ. Then Blair appears to join the Unholy Union, at least for this beat down

